<lb ed="B" n="0161a11"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="9"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0161a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">東山翼善寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>東山翼善寺<note place="inline">古剎　勅賜</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0161a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">沿革</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1301" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城東南北去所綂靈谷寺三十里正陽門十七里
<lb ed="B" n="0161a14"/>東城地晉謝太傅高臥東山及與張玄圍碁賭墅即其
<lb ed="B" n="0161a15"/>處梁資福院武帝建淨名院神僧寶公說法其間宋元
<lb ed="B" n="0161a16"/>改淨名寺　國朝正綂十年重建　賜今額所領小剎
<lb ed="B" n="0161a17"/>曰廣惠寺祈澤寺天寧寺雲居寺莊嚴寺</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">天王殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1807" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">天王殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">正佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1812" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">正佛殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1817" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左觀音殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右地藏殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1823" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右地藏
<lb ed="B" n="0161a19"/>殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">諸天殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1904" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">諸天殿<note place="inline">伍楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1909" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍殿<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右祖師殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1915" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右祖師殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">寶公殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a1921" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">寶公殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">靈官堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a2001" style="margin-left:2em">靈官堂<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">方丈</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a2006" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">方丈<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a2010" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">拾捌房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址拾畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161a2015" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址拾畆<note place="inline">東至駱子美民山　南至
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0161b" n="0161b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b01"/>官路　西至孫明山　北至楊家山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">公產</cb:mulu><head>【公產】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">地山</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161b0203" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">地山<note place="inline">共陸拾肆畆玖分貳厘</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">山水</cb:mulu><head>【山水】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">東山</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161b0303" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">東山<note place="inline">一名土山周四里高二十丈無巖石故曰土山輿地志云山下有湖自方山至京師此為
<lb ed="B" n="0161b04"/>半道今謂此山下道為半邏　晉石季龍入冠蔡謨所戍自土山至江乘　沈約郊居賦臨巽隅兮縱目
<lb ed="B" n="0161b05"/>即堆塚而流盻雖東山之崎嶁乃文靖之所宴</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">古蹟</cb:mulu><head>【古蹟】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">布塞亭</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161b0603" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">布塞亭<note place="inline">實錄吳景帝自會稽至曲阿有老翁干帝速行即日進至布塞亭孫綝迎於土山之
<lb ed="B" n="0161b07"/>半野</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">土山墅</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0161b0703" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">土山墅<note place="inline">秦符堅入<g ref="#CB04223"/>謝安命駕出土山墅張晏與張玄圍碁賭別墅即此時樓舘林木甚盛
<lb ed="B" n="0161b08"/>今無存</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【文】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">翼善寺碑記略</cb:mulu><head>翼善寺碑記略</head><byline cb:type="author">明禮部侍郎陳璉</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0161b10"/><p xml:id="pB29p0161b1001">土山有寺一區名曰東山淨名寺舊名資福院世傳吳景
<lb ed="B" n="0161b11"/>帝欲至金陵有老翁千帝速行起自會稽即日至布塞亭
<lb ed="B" n="0161b12"/>孫綝迎帝於土山之半墅而兹山之名始勝晉丞相謝安
<lb ed="B" n="0161b13"/>謝事棲止於斯姪謝玄入而問計丞相高臥於山間怡然
<lb ed="B" n="0161b14"/>無懼色玄復請遂命駕出張宴於土山之陽而茲山之名
<lb ed="B" n="0161b15"/>益振至梁武帝建名淨名院有神僧寶公者遍遊名山求
<lb ed="B" n="0161b16"/>棲息之所覩是山之勝遂講經說法於其間由是土山之
<lb ed="B" n="0161b17"/>勝益彰而淨名之境益顯矣下自宋元改額淨名寺以至
<lb ed="B" n="0161b18"/>於今殿廡僧舍年深<note n="0161b1801" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0161b1801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>毀及半惟佛殿一所獨存於是袁
<lb ed="B" n="0161b19"/>智海等募緣資財大作修崇巍然鼎創香火增崇僧行日
<lb ed="B" n="0161b20"/>盛誠足以表茲山之勝槩也正綂十年六月初十日題奏
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0162a" n="0162a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a01"/>禮部尚書胡濙奉　旨與做翼善禪寺因識其事於久遠
<lb ed="B" n="0162a02"/>云　正綂乙丑八月十五日</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">詩</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【詩】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">謝公墅歌</cb:mulu><head>謝公墅歌</head><byline cb:type="author">唐溫庭筠</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a04"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0162a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>朱雀航南繞香陌謝郎東墅連春碧鳩眠高柳日方融綺
<lb ed="B" n="0162a05"/>榭飄颻紫庭客文楸方罫花參差心陣未成星滿池四座
<lb ed="B" n="0162a06"/>無喧梧竹靜金蟬玉柄俱持<g ref="#CB02823"/>對局含情見千里都城<note n="0162a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0162a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a07"/>得　虵尾江南王氣繫疎襟未許符堅過淮水</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">土山</cb:mulu><head>土山</head><byline cb:type="author">唐李白</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a09"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0162a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>不向東山久薔薇幾度花白雲還自散明月落誰家</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">遊謝氏山亭</cb:mulu><head>遊謝氏山亭<note place="inline">謝靈運故</note></head><byline cb:type="author">唐李白</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a11"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0162a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>淪老臥江海再歡天地清病間久寂寞歲物徒芬榮借君
<lb ed="B" n="0162a12"/>西池遊聊以散我情掃雪松下去捫蘿石道行謝公池塘
<lb ed="B" n="0162a13"/>上春草颯<note n="0162a1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0162a1301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>生花枝拂人來山鳥向我鳴田家有美酒落
<lb ed="B" n="0162a14"/>日與之傾醉罷弄歸月遙欣稚子迎</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">土山</cb:mulu><head>土山</head><byline cb:type="author">明黃姬水</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a16"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0162a1601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>昔臥會稽客因<g ref="#CB12428"/>東山名宛然林泉趣猶是謝公情遠墅
<lb ed="B" n="0162a17"/>草全沒空門臺半傾誰知遊衍者偏解慰蒼生</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">東山</cb:mulu><head>東山</head><byline cb:type="author">明焦竑</byline>
<lb ed="B" n="0162a19"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0162a1901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>謝墅維青舫蕭臺接紫城到門雙樹立隔岸亂峰迎龍臥
<lb ed="B" n="0162a20"/>曾先達鴻<g ref="#CB07448"/>愧獨行蒼生誰繫望懷古重含情</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0162b" n="0162b"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0162b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">廣惠寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>廣惠寺</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0162b02"/><p xml:id="pB29p0162b0201" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城上方門外東城地西北去所領翼善寺一里去
<lb ed="B" n="0162b03"/>通濟門二十五里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0162b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0162b0403" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0162b0407" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址<g ref="#CB23001"/>畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0162b0411" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址<g ref="#CB23001"/>畆<note place="inline">東至官路　西至溝港　南至竹山村　北至官路</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0162b05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">祈澤寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>祈澤寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0162b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">沿革</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0162b0601" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城高橋門外東城地南去所領翼善寺十里西去
<lb ed="B" n="0162b07"/>正陽門三十里即祈澤山宋少帝景平元年建名祈澤
<lb ed="B" n="0162b08"/>治平寺會昌中廢南唐昇元間復宋治平間改祈澤寺
<lb ed="B" n="0162b09"/>元至正二年重建　國朝嘉靖十二年修葺為祈禱雨
<lb ed="B" n="0162b10"/>澤之所連彭城接青龍泉流澂徹如鏡</p></cb:div>
