<lb ed="B" n="0164a01"/><lg xml:id="lgB29p0164a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l>問年看井幹結夏閉山門路夾雙峰起泉流百道喧葡萄
<lb ed="B" n="0164a02"/>纏廢棟蛺蝶舞荒園窈窕堪棲隱<note n="0164a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">逢【CB】，逄【補編】</note><app n="0164a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">逢</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">逄</rdg></app>人未可言</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0164a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">雲居寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>雲居寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0164a04"/><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0401" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城高橋門外東城地西去正陽門四十里西南去
<lb ed="B" n="0164a05"/>所領翼善寺三十里鍾山舊有雲居寺及登覽詩今相
<lb ed="B" n="0164a06"/>去尚遠或移改無考因另入鍾山廢寺</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0164a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0703" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0707" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右伽藍殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0712" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右伽藍殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0718" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址參畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a0722" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址參畆
<lb ed="B" n="0164a08"/><note place="inline">東至官溝　南至官溝　西至八甲民田　北至太子山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
