<lb ed="B" n="0164a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">莊嚴寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>莊嚴寺<note place="inline">古剎</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0164a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">沿革</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a1101" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城高橋門外鳳城鄉東城地西去正陽門四十七
<lb ed="B" n="0164a12"/>里西南去所領翼善寺二十五里實錄謝尚以永和四
<lb ed="B" n="0164a13"/>年捨宅造莊嚴寺宋大明中路另造莊嚴寺于西藥園
<lb ed="B" n="0164a14"/>改為謝鎮西寺陳大建元年燬後五年豫州刺史程文
<lb ed="B" n="0164a15"/>秀修復孝宣帝勅改興嚴寺按元金陵新志謝尚莊嚴
<lb ed="B" n="0164a16"/>寺<note n="0164a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0164a1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>改興嚴寺今寺仍名莊嚴考謝尚宅又在城中竹
<lb ed="B" n="0164a17"/>格渡不知何年徙此<g ref="#CB07043"/>其寺唐貞觀<note n="0164a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【補編】</note><app n="0164a1701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">巳</rdg></app>酉間牛頭惠忠
<lb ed="B" n="0164a18"/>禪師移住建法堂元季復燬　國朝永樂間僧真常重
<lb ed="B" n="0164a19"/>建</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0164a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">山門</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a2003" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">山門<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a2007" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">佛殿<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB23001"/>楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左伽藍堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a2011" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左伽藍堂<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a2017" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">貳房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址拾伍畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0164a2021" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址拾伍畆
